data.description: Picture living in this welcoming brick rancher in Ivy Farms, complete with garage (with a utility sink), shed, and fenced-in yard.  Other features include new kitchen sink and countertops, replacement windows installed 2020, and a den with a fireplace, perfect  for a playroom or office. With 2 fireplaces, three bedrooms and two fully renovated full baths, this home offers plenty of living  space. Enjoy relaxing on the back deck ...but don’t be fooled; everything you need is a convenient drive away, including shops,  restaurants and retail establishments. Come see this serene home for yourself.
